OL,6,FPoliticians and officials from the are
OL,7,Fcalling for action to stop young
OL,8,Fpeople from using .
OL,10,FIt comes as the UK chancellor
OL,11,Fannounced s new tax on vapes would be
OL,12,Fintroduced in his budget.
OL,14,FThe separate levy will be applied to
OL,15,Fthe liquid in vapes, with the UK
OL,16,FTreasury expecting to raise more than
OL,17,F#500m a year by 2028-29 alongside an
OL,18,Fincrease in tobacco duty.
