OL,3,CCalls for Channel Islands to take more
OL,4,Caction to stop young people vaping
OL,6,F"It also means these young people are
OL,7,Fbecoming addicted to nicotine and we
OL,8,Fknow that can cause immediate effects
OL,9,Flike coughing but also anxiety."
OL,11,FDespite addiction concerns, Lucy Cave
OL,12,Ffrom the Guernsey Health Improvement
OL,13,FCommission explained: "We've had a
OL,14,Fvery high percentage (of young people)
OL,15,Fwho are saying they want to quit.
OL,17,F"It's really encouraging that it seems
OL,18,Fthat they do recognise the problems
OL,19,Fwith the addiction and that they do
OL,20,Fwant to look for that support."
