OL,3,CCalls for Channel Islands to take more
OL,4,Caction to stop young people vaping
OL,6,FJersey's Environment Minister, Deputy
OL,7,FSteve Luce, has affirmed that the
OL,8,Fgovernment want to stop young people
OL,9,Fvaping "before it becomes an epidemic".
OL,11,FHe said: "We know that youngsters are
OL,12,Fmanaging to get hold of these single-
OL,13,Fuse vapes, and vapes generally, but
OL,14,Fsingle-use in particular as they're a
OL,15,Flot less expensive.
OL,17,F"They're not necessarily directly
OL,18,Ftargeted (at young people), but they
OL,19,Fare nice to look at, the colours are
OL,20,Fbeing used to match clothing and crazy
OL,21,Fthings like that."
